item.title: Floor L-Sit progression
item.description: A small set of exercises which will help you progressing towards the floor L-Sit. This L-Sit progression shows the 6 mandatory achievements you need for an L-Sit, a compact sequence. See the L-Sit friendly list, an extensive collection of exercises facilitating the L-Sit position
